[center][u][b][size=20pt]DdsSpeced V1.0[/size][/b][/u]
Features
[ul][li]Real pking[/li] [li]Real working prayer.[/li] [li]All specs work with correct gfx.[/li] [li]Edited fight caves, Now only 7 waves decided to make it easier as many players found it hard.[/li] [li]Working lunar magic.[/li] [li]Working vengeance.[/li] [li]11 Quests.[/li] [li]Real following.[/li] [li]Syi proof.[/li] [li]Duping proof.[/li] [li]Fast exp rates, 1.2k per hit.[/li] [li]Changed pest control, More points per game + New rewards.[/li] [li]Fixed the Ancients glitch.
